metadata.name: Let The Show Begin
metadata.description:
Let The Show Begin-

In this piece, my aim was to express the fuel, desire and passion of my character (Inspired by P.T Barnum) An entertainer who found the noblest art in sharing happiness to the audience... 


The desire to succeed, to serve others, to keep on going, and in this case to put on the best performance.

 
Now ladies and gentlemen, let us put on the greatest show the world has ever seen. 

LET THE SHOW BEGIN!
